{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der n\u00e4chsten Woche j\u00e4hrt sich der Anschlag auf den Weihnachtsmarkt am Breitscheidplatz hier in Berlin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.840", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Anschlag\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.680", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das haben viele so empfunden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.000", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "war ein Anschlag auf uns alle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er hat Menschen aus dem Leben gerissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.480", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er hat Familien zerrissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.440", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und er hat unendliches Leid und Schmerz f\u00fcr die Opfer und Angeh\u00f6rigen gebracht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte deswegen sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.160", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den Opfern und Angeh\u00f6rigen gilt auch heute unser tief empfundenes Mitgef\u00fchl. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.240", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben an dieser Stelle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.120", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.320", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wirklich eine gemeinsame Haltung in diesem Haus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.600", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu der Trauer und auch der Anteilnahme ist allerdings im Laufe des letzten Jahres ein anderes Gef\u00fchl hinzugetreten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.000", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das mich sehr bedr\u00fcckt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist bei mir ein Gef\u00fchl von Scham und Schuld aufgetreten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "je mehr Tatsachen durch die Aufkl\u00e4rungsarbeiten \u00fcber das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.480", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was vorgefallen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.160", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an den Tag gebracht wurden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.080", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tatsachen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.600", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei denen wir uns eingestehen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.880", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir letztendlich bei der Verhinderung dieses Anschlags versagt haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.400", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber was besonders schlimm ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.520", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben auch noch versagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "angemessen auf die Opfer und Angeh\u00f6rigen zuzugehen und sie angemessen zu unterst\u00fctzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss hier und heute benannt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.840", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sind Missst\u00e4nde in der Terrorismusbek\u00e4mpfung ans Tageslicht gekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.120", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise die viel zu l\u00fcckenhafte oder sp\u00e4te Registrierung von Asylbewerbern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.480", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Zusammenarbeit der Sicherheitsbeh\u00f6rden der unterschiedlichen Ebenen unseres Landes ist es so gewesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es unklare Kompetenzen und auch Fehleinsch\u00e4tzungen gegeben hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fehleinsch\u00e4tzungen beispielsweise in Bezug auf die Frage der \u00dcberwachung von Gef\u00e4hrdern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade der T\u00e4ter vom Breitscheidplatz hat mehrere Straftaten begangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es wurde kein Haftbefehl beantragt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.600", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich muss an dieser Stelle sehr klar sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich das \u00e4ndern muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.400", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir Anfang n\u00e4chsten Jahres zu diesem Thema einen Parlamentarischen Untersuchungsausschuss einsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um diesen Sachverhalt weiter aufzukl\u00e4ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.440", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ziel dieses Untersuchungsausschusses muss es sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.040", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einerseits die Verantwortung der Bundesbeh\u00f6rden zu beleuchten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.400", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "andererseits Konsequenzen aus den Fehlern zu ziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss sich aber auch \u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.480", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie auf die Opfer von Terroranschl\u00e4gen und ihre Angeh\u00f6rigen zugegangen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.960", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Regierung und Beh\u00f6rden haben teilweise unbeholfen und ohne Routine reagiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich selber war bei dem Trauergottesdienst dabei. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir war nicht bewusst\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.360", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was sp\u00e4ter klar geworden ist\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass viele der Angeh\u00f6rigen zu diesem Zeitpunkt \u00fcberhaupt noch nicht wussten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob geliebte Menschen unter den Opfern waren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.120", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Finanziell erhielten viele nicht die Unterst\u00fctzung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.320", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sie erwartet oder dringend gebraucht h\u00e4tten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.320", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest nicht so unb\u00fcrokratisch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.560", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es notwendig gewesen w\u00e4re. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.640", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch dabei brauchen wir eine Ver\u00e4nderung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.960", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte heute den Angeh\u00f6rigen der Opfer vom Berliner Breitscheidplatz meinen allergr\u00f6\u00dften Respekt aussprechen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn sie haben die Kraft aufgebracht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.680", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit diesem schweren Schicksal umzugehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.640", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben aber auch noch die Kraft gehabt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich gegenseitig zu unterst\u00fctzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und sie haben sich zusammengeschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.400", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um in einem offenen Brief an die Bundeskanzlerin einen Handlungsbedarf des Gesetzgebers aufzuzeigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.000", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Respekt verdient; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.800", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es ist nicht selbstverst\u00e4ndlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.720", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Sache in dieser Weise zustande zu bringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.800", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt hier, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jedenfalls bei uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein offenes Ohr f\u00fcr die Anliegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.080", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kurt Beck ist der von der Bundesregierung Beauftragte f\u00fcr die Opfer der Hinterbliebenen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.480", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er hat sich in die Sache reingekniet und heute im Kabinett seinen Bericht vorgelegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.840", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er hat eine ganze Reihe von \u00c4nderungsvorschl\u00e4gen gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.200", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Bundesregierung annehmen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.960", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.120", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bereits eine umfangreiche Reform des Entsch\u00e4digungsrechtes von der Bundesregierung erarbeitet wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.880", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Punkt muss erweitert werden um die Aufarbeitung und die Erkenntnisse des Berichtes des Opferbeauftragten Kurt Beck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.200", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem ich an dieser Stelle daf\u00fcr ebenso danke wie der Bundesregierung f\u00fcr die Bereitschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "321.720", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Aspekte aufzunehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "321.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "324.400", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Einrichtung von einheitlichen Anlaufstellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "324.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "328.680", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine bessere finanzielle und unb\u00fcrokratischere Soforthilfe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "328.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "330.400", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "psychologische Betreuung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "330.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "332.320", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sind Erkenntnisse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "332.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.160", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir hier gesammelt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "333.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "334.520", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das alles sind Dinge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "334.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "337.680", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir in Zukunft brauchen werden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "337.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "338.400", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich hoffe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "338.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "339.200", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so selten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "339.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.080", 
   "id": "s000088", 
